{"title_page": "Mika\u00ebl Cantave", "text_new": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Mika\u00ebl Cantave\n| fullname = Mika\u00ebl Gabriel Cantave<ref name=CS>{{cite web|url=https://canadasoccer.com/?pid=608&t=profile&|title=Mika\u00ebl Cantave|publisher=Canada Soccer|accessdate=30 May 2018}}</ref>\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1996|10|25|df=yes}}<ref name=CS/>\n| image = \n| birth_place = [[Ottawa]], Canada<ref name=CS/>\n| height = 1.77m<ref>{{BDFutbol|22298|accessdate=30 May 2018}}</ref>\n| position = [[Midfielder]]\n| currentclub = [[CD Lealtad|Lealtad]]\n| clubnumber = 11\n| youthyears1 =           | youthclubs1 = FC Capital United\n| youthyears2 = 2012\u20132013 | youthclubs2 = [[FC Nantes|Nantes]]\n| youthyears3 = 2013      | youthclubs3 = Orvault SF\n| youthyears4 = 2013\u20132014 | youthclubs4 = [[USJA Carquefou]]\n| youthyears5 = 2014\u20132015 | youthclubs5 = [[Getafe CF|Getafe]]\n| years1 = 2015\u20132016 | clubs1 = [[CD Guadalajara (Spain)|Guadalajara<!-- It is not necessary to indicate this Guadalajara is the Spanish club because this footballer is not Mexican, so he cannot play for the other Guadalajara (the Mexican one where only Mexican players can play) -->]] | caps1 = 3 | goals1 = 0\n| years2 = 2016      | clubs2 = [[RSD Alcal\u00e1 B|Real Alcal\u00e1 B]] | caps2 = 7 | goals2 = 0<!-- http://ffmadrid.es/pnfg/NPcd/NFG_EstadisticasJugador?cod_primaria=3000227&jugador=5177918&codacta=802428&nueva_ventana= -->\n| years3 = 2017      | clubs3 = [[Albacete Balompi\u00e9 B|Albacete B]] | caps3 = 13 | goals3 = 0<!-- http://www.ffcm.es/pnfg/NPcd/NFG_EstadisticasJugador?cod_primaria=5000204&jugador=617523&codacta=239690&nueva_ventana= -->\n| years4 = 2017      | clubs4 = [[Lorca FC B|Lorca B]] | caps4 = 16 | goals4 = 0<!-- http://www.ffrm.es/pnfg/NPcd/NFG_EstadisticasJugador?cod_primaria=5000274&jugador=5815372&codacta=57977 -->\n| years5 = 2018      | clubs5 = [[Deportivo Rayo Cantabria|Rayo Cantabria]] | caps5 = 15 | goals5 = 2<!-- https://www.federacioncantabradefutbol.com/pnfg/NPcd/NFG_EstadisticasJugador?cod_primaria=5000274&jugador=5891415&codacta=63076&nueva_ventana= -->\n| years6 = 2018\u20132019 | clubs6 = [[CD Tropez\u00f3n|Tropez\u00f3n]] | caps6 = 24 | goals6 = 3\n| years7 = 2019\u2013     | clubs7 = [[CD Lealtad|Lealtad]] | caps7 = 22 | goals7 = 4\n| nationalyears1 = 2013 | nationalteam1 = [[Canada men's national under-17 soccer team|Canada U17]] | nationalcaps1 = 4 | nationalgoals1 = 0\n| nationalyears2 = 2018\u2013 | nationalteam2 = [[Haiti national football team|Haiti]] | nationalcaps2 = 9 | nationalgoals2 = 1\n| pcupdate = 4 February 2020\n| ntupdate = 4 February 2020\n}}\n'''Mika\u00ebl Gabriel \"Miki\" Cantave''' (born 25 October 1996) is a Haitian [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for Spanish club [[CD Lealtad|Lealtad]] and the [[Haiti national football team|Haiti national team]].\n\n==International career==\nCantave represented Canada at the [[2013 CONCACAF U-17 Championship]] and the [[2013 FIFA U-17 World Cup]]. In 2018, he switched allegiance to Haiti and made his international debut on 29 May 2018 in a friendly match against [[Argentina national football team|Argentina]].\n\n==Personal life==\nHis father is from [[Haiti]], while his mother is from the French overseas department of [[Guadeloupe]].<ref name=CS/>\n\n==Career statistics==\n===International goals===\n:''Haiti score listed first, score column indicates score after each Cantave goal.''<ref>{{cite web |title=Cantave, Mika\u00ebl |url=https://www.national-football-teams.com/player/71240/Mikael_Cantave.html |publisher=National Football Teams |accessdate=18 November 2018}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"font-size:85%; text-align: left;\" align=center\n|+ International goals by date, venue, cap, opponent, score, result and competition\n|-\n!scope=col|No.\n!scope=col data-sort-type=date|Date\n!scope=col|Venue\n!scope=col|Cap\n!scope=col|Opponent\n!scope=col|Score\n