 Cypriot Commanders - New weapons and materials for the Special Forces of GEF|date=20 March 2016|first=Doukas |last=Gaitatzis}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flagu|Finland}}\n| [[Special Jaegers]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| L\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hs.fi/kotimaa/a1424430676159|title=Armeija ostaa erikoisjoukoille Nato-yhteensopivat rynn\u00e4kk\u00f6kiv\u00e4\u00e4rit|date=20 February 2015|work=Helsingin Sanomat|accessdate=21 February 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150222124013/http://www.hs.fi/kotimaa/a1424430676159|archive-date=22 February 2015|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"| {{flagu|France}}\n| ''[[Recherche Assistance Intervention Dissuasion]]'' (RAID) police unit\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite magazine|language=fr|title=Du mat\u00e9riel au RAID|page=7|magazine=RAIDS|issn=0769-4814|publisher=Histoire & Collections|issue=322|date=March 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Commandement des Op\u00e9rations Sp\u00e9ciales]]'' (COS)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://lemamouth.blogspot.fr/2012/07/le-jeu-des-5-differences.html |title=Le d\u00e9tachement COS en VO |language=French |accessdate=13 July 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120726003027/http://lemamouth.blogspot.fr/2012/07/le-jeu-des-5-differences.html |archive-date=26 July 2012 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Compagnie de Commandement et de Transmissions'' (CCT)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.defense.gouv.fr/terre/mediatheque/phototheque/o